description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;SOUTH WIGHT MEDICAL PRACTICE  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Dispenser&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Full time &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated individual to manage the running of three dispensaries within our rural dispensing GP practice; supporting us in providing a professional and efficient service to our population of approximately 6000 patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duties will include dispensing of medication to patients, stock purchasing and control, ensuring Standard Operating Procedures are up to date and compliant and taking responsibility for the Dispensing Services Quality Scheme while maintaining effective financial management of the dispensary.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will have experience in running a dispensary and will have a dispensing qualification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Good organisational, communication and time management skills are essential, as is the ability to remain calm under pressure.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications and Requirements -  &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum of 2 years’ experience in a pharmacy or dispensary setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of NHS prescribing rules and regulations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NVQ 2 in Pharmacy Skills or equivalent qualification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience in leading a team is desirable but not essential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A full driving licence is essential.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities will include - &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining and developing relationships both with our patients and pharmaceutical company representatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Taking appropriate action for any updates and guidelines provided by MHRA and other healthcare providers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leading the dispensary team to deliver the agreed targets.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiating with Pharmaceutical suppliers to ensure maximum profit.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate records for controlled drugs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits – &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive Salary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;NHS Pension Scheme&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sick pay policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Health Service Discounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please visit southwightmedicalpractice.nhs.uk for further detail about our practice.&lt;/p&gt;
